RecordVariable.name: Dk_SampleInfo
RecordVariable.description: tag string at beginning of a data record; includes model of instrument and whether this is light or dark sample (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_SN
RecordVariable.description: serial number of the instrument (with the name, uniquely IDs instrument) (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Date
RecordVariable.description: temperature measured inside the MMC controller pressure housing (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Time
RecordVariable.description: hour of the day, in GMT floating point hours (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_NTR_CONC
RecordVariable.description: Nitrate concentration to 2 decimal places, as calculated by ISUS (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Salinity
RecordVariable.description: Salinity to 2 decimal places, as calculated by ISUS (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_RMS_Error
RecordVariable.description: Root Mean Square error of the ISUS-calculated concentration, to 6 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_T_Int
RecordVariable.description: temperature inside the ISUS instrument housing, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_T_Spec
RecordVariable.description: temperature of the ISUS spectrometer, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_T_Lamp
RecordVariable.longName: DarkSamp ISUS UV Light Source Temperature
RecordVariable.description: temperature of the ISUS UV light source, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Ref_Avg
RecordVariable.description: average reference channel measurement taken during the sample time, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Ref_StdDev
RecordVariable.longName: DarkSamp ISUS Reference Channel Std Dev
RecordVariable.description: variance of the Reference Channel measurement taken during the sample time, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_SW_Dark
RecordVariable.description: Sea-Water Dark calculation, to 2 decimal places, in spectrometer counts (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_Spec_Avg
RecordVariable.description: average value of all spectrometer channels, to 2 decimal places (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_C_CTD
RecordVariable.description: Reserved for future use: Conductivity measurement from an external CTD device (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_T_CTD
RecordVariable.description: Reserved for future use: Temperature measurement from an external CTD device (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_P_CTD
RecordVariable.description: Reserved for future use: Pressure measurement from an external CTD device (dark sample)

RecordVariable.name: Dk_RSRV1
